{"tid":276604,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[420] 大家最深刻既trip係咩？","createTime":"2017-06-09T02:53:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-09T04:04:56.000Z","uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9dfcbe3f1df66dbd2b63b998576d94ff5b5b0137","tid":276604,"uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T02:53:50.000Z","msg":"我有兩次發夢都好深刻啊<br />\n<br />\n有一次發夢我同3個朋友420完 去食放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地4個人一齊食左好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食放題食到完都仲係好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一次發夢我同朋友420完去行尖沙咀海旁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住維港既夜景 我覺得其實香港既夜景真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即使其實國家既夜景都無香港咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地又有咩深刻既trip可以分享下?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申: 以上全部都係我發夢夢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b09b0421862f9a590e9141c380b2c9c624d33e","tid":276604,"uid":56665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"試過係夜晚係泳池游水 涼陣陣 感受到水流係身邊流過 好似係咁被人摸 好舒服 同埋 游水游好左  好似同水做左好朋友咁 如果巴打識游水 一定要試試佢"},{"pid":"241ccaf398849fd40fb8ed1a3c31aaf9ee0cf58a","tid":276604,"uid":48514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T03:54:14.000Z","msg":"發夢上次食完飲酒嘔到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dba66621fa68194020ac51b08f916e9902c80f6","tid":276604,"uid":102961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T04:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過係夜晚係泳池游水 涼陣陣 感受到水流係身邊流過 好似係咁被人摸 好舒服 同埋 游水游好左  好似同水做左好朋友咁 如果巴打識游水 一定要試試佢</blockquote><br />\n<